  "title": "Business Development Executive (Modern Trade)",
  "description": "<p><u>Responsibilities</u></p><ul><li>Identify and source for new accounts and new business opportunities</li><li>Canvass for new customers (include cold call)</li><li>Build and maintain good working relationship with potential and existing client</li><li>Set and achieve sales targets individually and as a team.</li><li>Handle all customer enquiries</li><li>Liaise with operations teams to ensure timely delivery and servicing of dispenser machines</li><li>Manage and monitor customer' payment</li><li>Regular visits to customer to understand their requirements</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><u>Requirements</u></p><ul><li>Minimum 2-3 years' sales experience (B2B,B2C) in modern trade</li><li>Sales experience in kitchen equipment and water purifier</li><li>Aggressive & sales driven  </li><li>Proficiency in the use of MS word and excel</li><li>Able to work independently </li><li>5.5 work days </li><li>Singaporean preferred</li></ul><p><u>Salary Package</u><br /> - Basic Salary<br /> - Transport & Mobile Reimbursement*</p>",
